COG Recruiter 
Age: 35 yrs 
Race: Half-Orc 
Class: Fighter 
Rank: Adept 

![Garg Flayer.png](data:image/png;base64,)

Garg is a hard Recruiter, feeling it best to push the limits of everyone who wishes to join up with COG. He believes there is always a way to improve yourself, generally physically though mentally works too. Everyone has a story of when Garg beat them senseless before letting them join the Guild, some fond and some not so much…
